snippet.title: Deja-vu: A nightmare comes true (NES) Longplay [578]
snippet.description: Beaten for the first time, this is a really good kemco game in the same vein as shadowgate. I had gotten to the end of this game earlier in the day, but I think I did something wrong as I couldnt get rid of all my evidence and kept getting arrested. This time I stumbled into making it work thankfully. These games are always nice to play, maybe i'll do uninvited one day.
